{"tid":658834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(大棋局) 習近平曾找聶衛平學棋遭拒     聶衛平：怕他水平差","createTime":"2018-05-09T10:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T06:56:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"836b5ca60d1e2135ee51965fc8c43069f8c4ab5d","tid":658834,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com/mainland/focus/2013-12/2112284.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com%2Fmainland%2Ffocus%2F2013-12%2F2112284.html&d=phDuAanM8StDKKQ8E6Zu5NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6173dc4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com/mainland/focus/2013-12/2112284.html</a><br />\n<br />\n1980年代初，是聶衛平大放光輝的年代，他打破了日本棋手的壟斷，一度成為中國的民族英雄式的人物。<br />\n<br />\n耿飚訪日時，中國棋手正在日本參加中日圍棋擂台賽時，在習近平的牽線下，耿飚接見了棋手們，耿飚喜歡下棋，他要求習近平盡快學會圍棋，與他對弈。<br />\n<br />\n為此，習近平還專門找聶衛平學下棋。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;當時他(習近平)想學一點快速提高的辦法，&rdquo;聶衛平告訴《博客天下》，&ldquo;不過我沒教他，我怕他水平不行出去給我丟人。&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400978c148de371a9fc8223ccaeebe7f150a0d0d","tid":658834,"uid":157362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:10:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c450902f2da8c10f4e4546f299da36a065a60f8","tid":658834,"uid":43523,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"打破日本棋士統治應該要數曹薰鉉先"},{"pid":"a4c12e2ee43aa3426645e2c7ece807fa82833ea7","tid":658834,"uid":75137,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c450902f2da8c10f4e4546f299da36a065a60f8","tid":658834,"uid":43523,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"打破日本棋士統治應該要數曹薰鉉先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:12:57.000Z","msg":"吳清源呢"},{"pid":"18ec863b5f3eae4f31d60e386a57c18ca2e1c92e","tid":658834,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" clas